      <p class="body-lg">Born in Malaysia and expanding across Southeast Asia, our mission is to redefine daily carry rituals. We believe a device should have character, weight, and presence. Every silhouette is engineered for durability, every colorway is curated, and every draw is calibrated for raw performance.</p>
